did.abstract: Honors theses written by undergraduate students in the Stanford University Department of Political Science.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents note
scopecontent.p: The collection consists of honors theses written by undergraduate students in the Stanford University Department of Political Science.

accessrestrict.head: Access to Collection
accessrestrict.p: The collection is open for research; materials must be requested at least 48 hours in advance of intended use. No photocopies may be made.

userestrict.head: Publication Rights
userestrict.p: Copyright is retained by the creators for materials they have authored or otherwise produced. Transmission or reproduction of materials requires the written permission of the copyright owner.

prefercite.head: Preferred Citation note
prefercite.p: [Identification of item], Stanford University, Department of Political Science, Honors Theses (SC4-4493). Dept. of Special Collections and University Archives, Stanford University Libraries, Stanford, Calif.

acqinfo.head: Acquisition Information
acqinfo.p: This collection was transferred to the University Archives from the Department of Political Science in several accessions. Additional theses were transferred to the Stanford University Archives from the Hume Writing Center in 2011.
